{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"case"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"fsr"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}]}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Use AMD FidelityFX Super Resolution 1.0 upscaling for the viewport’s 3D buffer. The amount of scaling can be set using "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/Viewport\/scaling3dScale","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":". Values less than "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"1.0"},{"text":" will be result in the viewport being upscaled using FSR. Values greater than ","type":"text"},{"code":"1.0","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" are not supported and bilinear downsampling will be used instead. A value of ","type":"text"},{"code":"1.0","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" disables scaling."}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/Viewport\/Scaling3DMode-swift.enum\/fsr"},"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/swiftgodot\/viewport\/scaling3dmode-swift.enum\/fsr"]}],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Case","title":"Viewport.Scaling3DMode.fsr","modules":[{"name":"SwiftGodot"}],"symbolKind":"case","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"case"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"fsr","kind":"identifier"}],"externalID":"s:10SwiftGodot8ViewportC13Scaling3DModeO3fsryA2EmF"},"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot","doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/Viewport","doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/Viewport\/Scaling3DMode-swift.enum"]]},"references":{"doc://SwiftGodot/documentation/SwiftGodot/Viewport/Scaling3DMode-swift.enum":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/Viewport\/Scaling3DMode-swift.enum","title":"Viewport.Scali